Titolo: Strike Fleet

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Strike Fleet is a 1988 video game developed by Lucasfilm Games and published by Electronic Arts.  It was released for the Amiga, Apple II, Atari ST, Commodore 64, and MS-DOS.  Strike Fleet is the unofficial sequel to the war game PHM: Pegasus.
The player controls either the American or British Fleets over the course of ten scenarios, of which the last four can be played as a single campaign.  The player must fight against the navy and air force of various other nations including Argentina, the Soviet Union, and Iran.